# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:514
msgid "Soft Light"
msgstr "Lumină moale"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:514
msgid "Gentle contrast curve; softer than Overlay."
msgstr "Curba de contrast blândă; mai moale decât Suprapunere."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:515
msgid "Hard Light"
msgstr "Lumină dură"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:515
msgid "Stronger, edgy contrast using the upper layer to drive the change."
msgstr ""
"Contrast mai puternic, ascuțit, folosind stratul superior pentru a conduce "
"schimbarea."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:516
msgid "Difference"
msgstr "Diferență"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:516
msgid ""
"Absolute difference between layers. Creates inverted/psychedelic colors; "
"useful for alignment."
msgstr ""
"Diferența absolută între straturi. Creează culori inversate/psihadelice; "
"util pentru aliniere."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:517
msgid "Exclusion"
msgstr "Excludere"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:517
msgid "Softer version of Difference with less contrast."
msgstr "Versiune mai moale a Diferenței cu contrast redus."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:520
msgid "**Notes**"
msgstr "**Note**"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:522
msgid ""
"Blend modes affect **color**, while alpha (the :guilabel:`Alpha` property) "
"affects **transparency**. You can use both."
msgstr ""
"Modurile de amestec afectează **culoarea**, în timp ce alfa (proprietatea :"
